  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "00fad510382eb8e4f65e6c653e420ab14ca9d047c6251caadc11ebbe5f3c277a": "[?], get over here! We need to go. Now!",
    "1d30938f11b04e313a8186a7a12b5e576357158d5456b0833c520f877b68604a": "Well met, [?]. Do you have your weapon?",
    "2876293a70c1ad8ec1c61bb6152b6986e4305a813be1909fc9c70bbbd0efe137": "Oh, and [?], I would appreciate it if you could avoid mentioning the stuff about Ivandis Seergaze to Ivan. One day he will have to bear that burden. But for now, he has enough weight on his shoulders.",
    "2c84aa2a3c5a8bfb4f39c08857e3e0551d81c6562dccc1758a42c6e53433b761": "Indeed. Let's get it done. [?], meet me outside the church in Slepe. We're going to pay Damien a little visit.",
    "4bf8f9e8638f3d21cb2f115d6ea528a65f5081df0b34f47d4e70ff80846d978b": "Good work [?]. Did it all go okay?",
    "528910b2b99d9e6a1adcf89e4915befb51033b3ee13840f6f51d2f2444fff3b4": "[?], I would appreciate it if you could escort Ivan down to Burgh de Rott.",
    "5957a085ec3a2dd580122bd8ef616dd79977d1c8b156f7e111605f0caf43ca29": "Well [?], you have certainly excelled yourself in this task. I believe you may soon be true Myreque material.",
    "5ceaf108cfcdf61de7a2c00f6c35c234ae232a41479d8eb1d8fb9c78f1f93c60": "Well met, [?]. How goes it?",
    "6a22c4b2d6d901a23f1134a571422ea7418532cc9237d55b02043420041d4617": "Very well. Meet me there, [?]. Let's see if we can find out what's going on.",
    "6ee57a3ce36760366d8592272ed16c809c0a394f520aa9eb1811c971888e70d2": "[?]! Safalaan! We need to go!",
    "7a1f4b739e83dea964d0b4e9a64cfac56d8d7e583bfb317f61d9d900318807ca": "Myreque prevail [?].",
    "80f63ffd9106da67b120774882c729759f3b711bea2d4bad986b5f8e04cf3c8c": "And formally, sister to Ranis Drakan, before [?] here came along.",
    "8dd83441d011692b75e6a850324d112e1b16b591e36e8f8e047d8934a7903968": "Go back to Paterdomus, Ivan. [?] and I will handle it.",
    "93acf5e3ef1db115479dccf044fe7ad425f5a787ac8143953958095610704a28": "Well met, [?]. I'm guessing you have your weapon?",
    "9c160a59a573b46c62a8e910e00686581963766637a60ee62a1f0d6eec87bbe4": "Speaking of [?], about that other matter I mentioned in my message...",
    "a11dee1e776cf5a8b322d7a7f75560f7e7f993cea235a9298d01950c3dadb94d": "Well, it seems that you have more than proven yourself worthy, [?]. Safalaan himself has recommended you for a promotion to the rank of a private within the Myreque!",
    "a40afdfe6f333d1237d52ced00ecef9e53dcea265704798ed7ba76da38f5cd37": "Hmm. Well [?] has to go with you. I want him there in case Vanescula here tries anything.",
    "aa6347403736a86dd4019de703a3c2c7f1305a43f7e63a2234c691afe3041acc": "Perhaps their encounter with you scared them off, [?].",
    "b026c971a9238360ec0b7b9b1b69db9fa5c3988a5015eda67c4a6e8c62266ff3": "Ah, [?], you're back. Good to see you made it okay.",
    "c26ebee3e9762642cdfe4519488a5643e2322222f1bcfb837f2a5fdad0b0b7d4": "Now's not the time for chat, [?]. You're meant to be watching Safalaan and Vanescula.",
    "ca6c9ac25e3351952b9e57076239a6ca32633b5f0225548657476ae824d9d1a0": "Well met, [?].",
    "e0502492629da3241f41ba7ddd2aebd70f072ca5e0f46b725ee611c0aca472ae": "I'll probably have to meet up with Safalaan at some point, so we can discuss strategies. This war is far from over, [?]. There's plenty of time to contribute so don't worry about that.",
    "f8f2a54378e6af304eb0c14b2cc1714b3889099d025388302d306e584f73fda3": "Indeed. But Ivan, you shouldn't be out here. It's not safe for you. Head back to the temple, let [?] and I take it from here.",
    "ff1c340db26e28def69a1df347d6485862143165be6ce6cc6bc0a95ce948d8aa": "Well met, [?]. It's good to see you again."
  }
}